Installation
============

```
export PREFIX="~/.local/opt/carbon/"

cc src/make.c -o make
./make
tar -xvf carbon-*.tgz -C $PREFIX
```

It's also possible to download a pre-compiled package for your CPU's architecture and OS from: <https://github.com/sparky-game/carbon/releases>.
Then, you just must extract the contents of the package into your desired `PREFIX`.
